  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4467081/" class="title-link">《庄子奥义》“全息结构论”于吾国文学史之意义</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4467081"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/wujianwen1222/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u2169106-7.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/wujianwen1222/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">卜雨</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-11-16"
      class="main-meta">2010-11-16 16:17:48</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4467081_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  　　《庄子奥义》一书为上海张远山君新出之巨作。其中各篇解析，堪称绝妙。然庄子之奥义，古人或能悟得。唯论七篇之全息结构，前人未曾窥见。特别是作者所创绘之“南溟弔詭圖”，精彩绝伦，实是此书之最佳创造。此一结论于吾国文学史，实有莫大之价值。  　　吾国艺术之思维模...

