  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1515759">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1515759/" class="title-link">阴谋论</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1515759"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/zenmenow/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1266583-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/zenmenow/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">zenmenow</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-10-05"
      class="main-meta">2008-10-05 16:13:12</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1515759_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  阴谋论在古典考辨中得到了新的应用。 远山先生是我敬仰的人，他的学识、他的为人，但本书中的那种浓烈的偏执与强迫推理实在让我窒息。 当你太爱一样东西时，它于你就会成为一种偏执，进而就会影响到你的Judgement。我想对庄子的热爱很多时候也影响了远山先生的判断。 而对于我...

