  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="2979442">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2979442/" class="title-link">我读这本书</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2979442"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/leanwang/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1649527-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/leanwang/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">黄孝阳</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-02-05"
      class="main-meta">2010-02-05 23:42:22</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2979442_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                   学术是知识的累积，更是智慧之物，是站在巍巍高山，俯瞰万千河流，看那日月经天。尤其对经典的解读，更要有一种独与天地精神往来的气魄，而非是埋首于故纸，于细微末节处下功夫，为考证一字之偏旁、音训动辄千言。陈寅恪讲，“所谓真了解者，必神游冥想，与立说之古人，处于同...

